      "content": "it's more than just \"sensitivity\" though. i can literally see the geometry of these patterns when i close my eyes. it feels physical, like a sequence written into my cells. i don't want to just \"ground\" myself, i want to actually unlock the data that's already there. are there specific types of deep meditation that help bypass the conscious mind and talk directly to the biological level?",
